{
  "id": "adv_card_suz_09_03",
  "title": "成宮すず 3話 ハッピーバレンタインですわ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――次の日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The next day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1400,
          "startTime": 1.4
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "お、お疲れ様ですわ。今日は……そ、その\n打ち合わせの続き、でした、わよね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ good work. Today is… th-the\ncontinuation of the meeting‚ right…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.0216849773,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（先日の一件以来、すっかりヤバい人認定されて）\n（しまったみたいだな……。早く弁明しないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ever since that incident the other day‚ she's completely labeled me）\n（ as a weirdo… I need to clear things up quickly.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.0666667064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "すず、やっと分かったんだよ\nどうやら俺達はずっとすれ違ってたみたいだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu‚ I finally figured it out.\nWe seem to have been misunderstanding each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.6329922453,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "すれ違い……？　どういうことですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Misunderstanding…? What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9333333731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなから聞いたんだよ。「すずがバレンタイン\nチョコのCMに出演するんだと喜んでいた」ってな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from everyone. \"Suzu was so happy that\nshe was going to be appear in a Valentine's Day chocolate CM.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0000000398,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "何も間違っていませんわよね？\nそれの何がおかしいんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not wrong‚ am I?\nWhat's so strange about that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.8702538628,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "バレンタイン時期に放映されるとは言ったけど\nチョコのCMとは言ってないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I said it would air around Valentine's Day‚\nbut I didn't say it was a chocolate CM.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.3644671105,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "え",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.0333303213,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ポテトチップスのCMだって説明しただろ？\nどうやら浮かれて聞いてなかったみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I explained that it was a potato chip CM‚ didn't I?\nIt seems you were too excited to listen properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8047775682,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんな……私、ずっと……\nチョコのCMだと勘違いを……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No way… I‚ all this time…\nmisunderstood it as a chocolate CM…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.4999990225,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "あら……？　ま、待ってくださいまし。勘違いだった\nということは、先日のただれた一件は……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh…? W-Wait a minute. If it was a misunderstanding‚\nthen that lewd incident the other day…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.2333323558,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ただれた一件って……。ポテトチップスを二枚重ねて\nアヒルの口みたいにする遊びのことを言ったんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That lewd incident…? I was talking about the playing stacking two potato chips\nand making a duck beak.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.4464446791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ……なるほど……\nそれなら確かに、小学生もやりそうですわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I see…\nThat certainly sounds like something elementary school kids would do…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.033329304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お、おい、すず？　どうした？\nそんな虚ろな目をして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Hey‚ Suzu? What's wrong?\nWhy are you looking so vacant…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.033329304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "今までの私の言動の数々を思い出して悶絶している\nだけなので、気にしないでくださいまし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm just agonizing over all the things I've said and done‚\nso please don't worry about it…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.872406492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……やっと落ち着きましたわ\nご迷惑をおかけして申し訳ありませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… I've finally calmed down.\nI'm sorry for causing you trouble.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.2341861874,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、みんなの誤解を解くのは大変だったけどな\n特に沙季は物凄く冷たい目をしてたからな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was certainly tough clearing up everyone's misunderstanding.\nEspecially Saki‚ she was giving me the coldest stare…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.9666626374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "とはいえ、CM内容の勘違いに気付かなかった俺も\n悪かった。やっぱりチョコのCMの方が良かったか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That being said‚ it's also my fault for unnoticing your misunderstanding about the CM content.\nWould you have preferred a chocolate CM after all?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.833329304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そんなことはありませんわ！\n確かに驚きはしましたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-That's not true!\nI was surprised‚ of course…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "大好きなポテトチップスのお仕事なんですもの\n嬉しいに決まっていますわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's a job for potato chips I really like!\nSurely I'm happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2867232645,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "良かった。俺ももともと、すずのためにあるような\n企画だと思ってたからな。期待してるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad. I also thought it was a project perfect for you\nfrom the beginning. I'm looking forward to it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.204401344,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "お任せなさい！　ここからは気持ちを切り替えて……\nばっちり決めてみせますわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Leave it to me! From now on‚ I'll switch gears and…\nI'll make sure to do a great job!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.1000010569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――The day of the CM shoot",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.6333338816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.7533308346
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.7533308346
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "ポーズはこれで……あとは決め台詞ですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The pose is like this… Now for the final line.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 160.6000076691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "「食べたら……羽ばたけますわよ？\n天使のポテトチップス、新発売！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"If you eat them… you'll be able to fly?\nAngel's potato chips‚ now on sale!\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.1666667063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "……オーケーですか？　ありがとうございます！\nえ、何か別パターンをアドリブで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is this okay? Thank you!\nEh‚ you want me to ad-lib a different pattern?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.2333221832,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 182.7833287953
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.0333287953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね、それなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.8333287953,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_photostudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "photostudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 188.2333287953
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_09_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "「食べちゃダメと言われるほど\n美味しくなるのは……なぜなんでしょうね？」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "\"The more you're told not to eat them‚\nthe more delicious they become… I wonder why?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.2333333333,
